www.cantocaptions.com

2
00:01:30,406 --> 00:01:33,659
(yue)（遙遠嘅大陸北方盡頭）
(en) (The northern end of the distant continent)

3
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:37,009
(yue)（我抵達咗被世人稱為天國嘅地方）
(en) (I have arrived at the place known by the world as the Kingdom of Heaven)

4
00:01:37,009 --> 00:01:39,759
(yue)（"靈魂長眠之地"）
(en) (The land where souls sleep in eternal peace)

5
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:42,430
(yue)（嗰度係個聚集咗好多靈魂嘅地方）
(en) (That is the place where many souls are gathered)

6
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:45,100
(yue)（我同過去嘅戰友對話）
(en) (I converse with my comrades of the past)

7
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,536
(yue)（大魔法使弗蘭梅）
(en) (Grand Magician Franmei)

8
00:02:00,122 --> 00:02:00,953
(yue)芙莉蓮
(en) Flilian

9
00:02:08,751 --> 00:02:10,597
(yue)已經可以見到皇都喇
(en) We can already see the imperial capital.

10
00:02:10,771 --> 00:02:13,664
(yue)我哋幾個同勇者一齊凱旋而歸
(en) The few of us, along with the hero, return in triumph.

11
00:02:13,715 --> 00:02:15,650
(yue)全國上下而家一定好興奮
(en) The whole country is surely very excited right now.

12
00:02:18,050 --> 00:02:20,297
(yue)返到去之後，就要開始揾嘢做喇
(en) After returning, we must start finding something to do.

13
00:02:21,198 --> 00:02:23,544
(yue)乜你已經開始考慮緊呢樣嘢嗱？
(en) What, have you already started thinking about that?

14
00:02:23,637 --> 00:02:25,243
(yue)呢樣嘢好緊要㗎
(en) That is very important.

15
00:02:25,294 --> 00:02:28,396
(yue)就算我哋已經打贏咗魔王都要繼續生活
(en) Even after defeating the Demon King, we must continue living.

16
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,460
(yue)之後落嚟嘅人生仲有好長㗎
(en) The life ahead of us is still very long.

17
00:02:32,249 --> 00:02:33,440
(yue)要揾嘢做
(en) We need to find something to do.

18
00:02:34,058 --> 00:02:36,323
(yue)如果份工可以隨時飲酒就好喇
(en) It would be great if the job allowed for drinking anytime.

19
00:02:36,624 --> 00:02:37,984
(yue)你唔係僧侶嚟咩？
(en) Aren't you a monk?

20
00:02:40,561 --> 00:02:41,800
(yue)噉講又係𠸏
(en) That's just like you.

21
00:02:44,453 --> 00:02:47,440
(yue)芙莉蓮，你跟住落嚟嘅人生
(en) Flilian, the life that lies ahead for you

22
00:02:47,772 --> 00:02:50,049
(yue)一定會比我哋可以想象得到嘅
(en) will certainly be beyond what we can imagine

23
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,850
(yue)更加漫長得多啊嗬？
(en) much longer, huh?

24
00:03:02,438 --> 00:03:07,971
(yue)《葬送的芙莉蓮》
(en) “The Funeral of Flilian”

25
00:03:30,914 --> 00:03:33,004
(yue)勇者欣梅爾
(en) Hero Xinmel

26
00:03:33,029 --> 00:03:34,554
(yue)戰士艾冉
(en) Warrior Airan

27
00:03:34,825 --> 00:03:36,007
(yue)僧侶海塔
(en) Monk Haita

28
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,867
(yue)魔法使芙莉蓮
(en) Mage Flilian

29
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:43,154
(yue)你哋今次成功打敗咗魔王做得好好
(en) You all did a great job defeating the Demon King this time.

30
00:03:43,514 --> 00:03:47,281
(yue)從此，世界將會迎嚟和平嘅時代
(en) Henceforth, the world will enter an era of peace.

31
00:04:03,325 --> 00:04:07,109
(yue)聽講國王陛下
會整我哋嘅雕像放喺廣場嗰度啊
(en) I heard that His Majesty the King will commission statues of us to be placed in the square.

32
00:04:07,815 --> 00:04:12,589
(yue)不過，個雕像究竟可唔可以真實還原到
我呢個咁俊俏不凡嘅樣呢？
(en) However, can the statue truly replicate my exceptionally handsome looks?

33
00:04:12,652 --> 00:04:14,358
(yue)講真我好有保留囖
(en) Honestly, I have my reservations.

34
00:04:15,332 --> 00:04:17,078
(yue)佢哋班人真係現實
(en) Those people are really down-to-earth.

35
00:04:17,129 --> 00:04:20,445
(yue)開始旅程嗰陣
明明只係畀咗十個銅幣我哋咋
(en) At the beginning of our journey, they only gave us ten copper coins.

36
00:04:22,332 --> 00:04:24,232
(yue)好喇，算數啦，芙莉蓮
(en) Alright, it's a deal, Flilian.

37
00:04:24,283 --> 00:04:26,951
(yue)橫掂而家可以噉樣免費任飲酒
(en) Now, you can freely drink without charge like this.

38
00:04:27,128 --> 00:04:28,955
(yue)噉樣已經夠啦，係咪啊？
(en) Isn't that enough?

39
00:04:29,434 --> 00:04:30,824
(yue)你個酒肉和尚
(en) You meat-eating monk.

40
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:40,555
(yue)旅程已經完結喇
(en) The journey has come to an end.

41
00:04:41,344 --> 00:04:42,209
(yue)講得啱啊
(en) That's right.

42
00:04:43,455 --> 00:04:45,577
(yue)我哋嘅冒險到呢度終於都完喇
(en) Our adventure has finally ended here.

43
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:48,270
(yue)已經十年喇
(en) It's been ten years.

44
00:04:49,078 --> 00:04:51,324
(yue)喺呢段時間發生咗好多事
(en) A lot has happened during these years.

45
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:54,148
(yue)我記得出發嗰一日
(en) I remember the day we departed.

46
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:57,057
(yue)欣梅爾同艾冉對國王陛下不敬
(en) Xinmel and Airan were disrespectful to His Majesty the King.

47
00:04:57,067 --> 00:04:58,388
(yue)爭啲被處死
(en) They nearly faced execution.

48
00:04:58,745 --> 00:05:01,648
(yue)一唔小心我哋嘅冒險可能會喺嗰度完
(en) Had we not been cautious, our adventure might have ended there.

49
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:55,836
(yue){\an8}郁手
(en) {\an8}Move hand

50
00:05:03,031 --> 00:05:04,989
(yue)海塔仲試過因為宿醉一啲用都冇
(en) Haita even once was completely incapacitated by a hangover.

51
00:05:05,047 --> 00:05:06,522
(yue)連路都行唔到啊
(en) He couldn't even walk.

52
00:05:11,266 --> 00:05:14,506
(yue)你塊面青到好似不死族噉喎，冇嘢吖嘛？
(en) Your face is as pale as that of the undead; is something wrong?

53
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:17,180
(yue)-唔得喇
-都估到你㗎喇
(en) - No way.
- I knew it.

54
00:05:17,231 --> 00:05:19,784
(yue)佢每個禮拜都會有一次醉到噉
(en) He gets that drunk once every week.

55
00:05:19,835 --> 00:05:21,769
(yue)喺呢方面嘅話，我就好優秀
(en) In that aspect, I'm truly excellent.

56
00:05:21,794 --> 00:05:24,032
(yue)-你爭啲畀寶箱怪食咗嗰陣
-好黑啊，好得人驚啊
(en) - When you were almost eaten by the treasure chest monster,
- it was pitch dark and terrifying.

57
00:05:24,056 --> 00:05:25,434
(yue)我哋有諗過抌低你㗎
(en) We even thought about taking you down.

58
00:05:25,494 --> 00:05:28,516
(yue)-同你講咗好多次係陷阱啦，仲中招
-你哋唔好企喺度快啲過嚟幫下我啦，好驚
(en) - We told you countless times it was a trap, but you still fell for it.
- Don't just stand there; come help me quickly, I'm terrified.

59
00:05:28,567 --> 00:05:30,114
(yue)-蠢成咁不如抌低佢喇
-唔好，唔好食我啊
(en) - You're so foolish, might as well take him down.
- No, don't, don't eat me!

60
00:05:35,259 --> 00:05:36,340
(yue)真係吖
(en) Really.

61
00:05:36,847 --> 00:05:38,729
(yue)淨係諗到啲搞笑嘅回憶啊
(en) All I can recall are these hilarious memories.

62
00:05:40,058 --> 00:05:41,363
(yue)不過真係好開心啊
(en) But it truly brings me joy.

63
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:45,220
(yue)我好慶幸可以同你哋一齊冒險係真㗎
(en) I am truly grateful to have adventured with you all.

64
00:05:46,125 --> 00:05:47,587
(yue)冇錯，講得啱啊
(en) That's right, exactly.

65
00:05:47,863 --> 00:05:49,999
(yue)雖然呢段冒險嘅時間有啲短
(en) Although this adventure was somewhat short,

66
00:05:50,610 --> 00:05:53,220
(yue)你話有啲短？你喺度講咩啊？
(en) You say it's short? What are you even saying?

67
00:05:53,244 --> 00:05:54,676
(yue)成十年喎
(en) It's been ten years!

68
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:58,220
(yue)你睇下海塔，已經由後生仔變咗做大叔喇
(en) Look at Haita; he has transformed from a young lad into an old man.

69
00:05:58,271 --> 00:05:59,517
(yue)你噉講嘢㗎？
(en) Is that what you're saying?

70
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,449
(yue)佢本來就係大叔
(en) He was always an old man.

71
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,993
(yue)連你都噉講？
(en) Even you say that?

72
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:11,245
(yue)差唔多要開始喇
(en) It's almost time to begin.

73
00:06:19,767 --> 00:06:22,080
(yue)好似係叫半世紀流星，係咪啊？
(en) It appears to be called the half-century meteor, doesn't it?

74
00:06:22,876 --> 00:06:25,730
(yue)50年先會出現一次嘅流星雨
(en) A meteor shower that occurs only once every 50 years.

75
00:06:26,973 --> 00:06:29,973
(yue)好啱用嚟做揭開呢個和平時代嘅序幕啊
(en) It's ideal for ushering in this era of peace.

76
00:06:32,793 --> 00:06:33,893
(yue)真係好靚啊
(en) It's truly beautiful.

77
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,921
(yue)喺呢個城鎮好難睇得清啊
(en) In this town, it's difficult to see clearly.

78
00:06:36,972 --> 00:06:38,773
(yue)我而家喺度感動緊㗎
(en) I am deeply moved right now.

79
00:06:38,852 --> 00:06:40,244
(yue)唔好破壞個氣氛啦
(en) Don't ruin the mood.

80
00:06:42,324 --> 00:06:43,270
(yue)係噉，下次
(en) Alright, next time...

81
00:06:45,401 --> 00:06:48,870
(yue)50年之後，我知有個睇得更加清楚嘅地方
(en) In 50 years, I know of a place where the view is even clearer.

82
00:06:48,921 --> 00:06:49,934
(yue)我帶你哋去吖
(en) I'll take you there.

83
00:06:53,542 --> 00:06:54,434
(yue)笑咩啊？
(en) What are you laughing at?

84
00:06:54,666 --> 00:06:55,398
(yue)冇
(en) Nothing.

85
00:06:55,956 --> 00:06:56,979
(yue)咩事都冇啊
(en) There's really nothing.

86
00:06:58,829 --> 00:06:59,820
(yue)就噉話啦
(en) That's what I meant.

87
00:07:00,671 --> 00:07:02,069
(yue)大家一齊去睇
(en) Let's all go and see.

88
00:07:24,707 --> 00:07:26,354
(yue)係噉，喺度講再見喇
(en) Alright then, it's time to say goodbye here.

89
00:07:26,992 --> 00:07:28,680
(yue)跟住你有咩打算啊？
(en) What are you planning to do next?

90
00:07:29,219 --> 00:07:31,150
(yue)我諗住繼續收集魔法
(en) I intend to keep collecting magic.

91
00:07:31,617 --> 00:07:35,189
(yue)我預計會用一百年左右行勻成個中央諸國
(en) I anticipate spending roughly a hundred years traveling throughout the central nations.

92
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,253
(yue)不過，我間中會揾下你哋𠸏
(en) However, I'll occasionally seek you out.

93
00:07:42,529 --> 00:07:45,197
(yue)精靈嘅時間觀念真係好難理解
(en) The elves' perception of time is truly hard to understand.

94
00:07:45,221 --> 00:07:47,840
(yue)咪係囖，佢究竟可以生存幾耐呢？
(en) Indeed, just how long can they survive?

95
00:07:48,488 --> 00:07:51,417
(yue)無論係50年定100年，對佢嚟講
(en) Whether it's 50 or 100 years, to them

96
00:07:51,528 --> 00:07:53,700
(yue)或者都只係一啲微不足道嘅時間
(en) is merely a negligible span of time.

97
00:08:44,295 --> 00:08:46,424
(yue)你話暗黑龍嘅角？
(en) Are you referring to the Dark Dragon's horn?

98
00:08:46,502 --> 00:08:49,208
(yue)我哋鋪頭冇賣呢樣嘢啝
(en) Our store doesn't carry such an item.

99
00:08:49,348 --> 00:08:53,283
(yue)就算係暗黑龍都已經二三十年冇見過喇
(en) Even the Dark Dragon hasn't been seen for twenty or thirty years.

100
00:08:53,307 --> 00:08:55,395
(yue)係呀？噉就麻煩喇
(en) Really? That could be problematic.

101
00:08:55,485 --> 00:08:57,108
(yue)召喚嗰陣要用㗎
(en) It's needed for summoning.

102
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:02,478
(yue)係喎，之前係魔王城執到嘅角
(en) Right, it was the horn we obtained from the Demon King's castle.

103
00:09:03,126 --> 00:09:05,045
(yue)應該仲放喺欣梅爾嗰度
(en) It should still be kept with Xinmel.

104
00:09:05,970 --> 00:09:09,350
(yue)硬係覺得佢散發住好邪惡嘅氣息啊
(en) I just feel that it emanates a truly sinister aura.

105
00:09:09,403 --> 00:09:11,220
(yue)但係應該對人冇害㗎嗬？
(en) But it probably doesn't harm people, does it?

106
00:09:11,244 --> 00:09:12,343
(yue)我唔知啊
(en) I don't know.

107
00:09:12,394 --> 00:09:13,947
(yue)連你都唔知呀？
(en) Even you don't know?

108
00:09:14,912 --> 00:09:17,456
(yue)就嚟又到半世紀流星嘅時候
(en) Soon, it will be time for the half-century meteor again.

109
00:09:17,507 --> 00:09:18,963
(yue)順便睇下佢點樣啦
(en) Might as well see how it turns out.

110
00:09:25,185 --> 00:09:28,501
(yue)同上次嚟嗰陣比條街真係唔同咗好多
(en) The street has changed so much compared to the last time.

111
00:09:43,165 --> 00:09:44,907
(yue)我記得喺呢度附近㗎喎
(en) I recall it being around here.

112
00:09:45,585 --> 00:09:46,794
(yue)芙莉蓮？
(en) Flilian?

113
00:09:47,865 --> 00:09:48,834
(yue)欣梅爾？
(en) Xinmel?

114
00:09:55,893 --> 00:09:57,155
(yue)你老咗好多啊
(en) You've aged significantly.

115
00:09:57,212 --> 00:09:59,167
(yue)講嘢咁過分㗎
(en) You speak too harshly.

116
00:10:01,068 --> 00:10:04,560
(yue)就算我而家老咗，都仲幾俊俏吖
(en) Even though I'm old now, I'm still quite dashing.

117
00:10:06,395 --> 00:10:08,575
(yue)已經50年冇見喇
(en) It's been 50 years since we last met.

118
00:10:08,622 --> 00:10:11,404
(yue)你個樣仲係同以前一模一樣
(en) You still look exactly the same as before.

119
00:10:12,113 --> 00:10:15,396
(yue)我仲以為呢一世都唔會再見到你喇
(en) I had thought I would never see you again in this life.

120
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:19,917
(yue)半世紀流星呀？
(en) The half-century meteor, huh?

121
00:10:19,968 --> 00:10:21,484
(yue)好令人懷念啊
(en) It's so reminiscent.

122
00:10:21,846 --> 00:10:24,876
(yue)仲有就係關於係魔王城執到嘅嗰樣嘢
(en) And also, about that thing we retrieved from the Demon King's castle.

123
00:10:24,927 --> 00:10:27,386
(yue)你係咪講咁黑龍嘅角啊？
(en) Are you referring to the Dark Dragon's horn?

124
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:30,589
(yue)關於呢樣嘢，我從來都冇忘記過
(en) I have never forgotten about it.

125
00:10:30,613 --> 00:10:34,190
(yue)因為佢一直喺個櫃裏面散發邪惡嘅氣息
(en) Because it has always exuded an evil aura from within the cabinet.

126
00:10:34,826 --> 00:10:36,123
(yue)真係唔好意思
(en) I'm truly sorry.

127
00:10:36,737 --> 00:10:40,175
(yue)其實你求其揾個倉庫
放佢入去唔理佢咪得囖
(en) Actually, you could simply find a warehouse and put it away, and not worry about it.

128
00:10:42,163 --> 00:10:43,730
(yue)噉樣點得嗄？
(en) That won't do, will it?

129
00:10:47,344 --> 00:10:52,043
(yue)對你嚟講，或者佢可能
只係一樣隨便寄放喺我度嘅嘢
(en) To you, it might simply be something you casually leave with me,

130
00:10:52,094 --> 00:10:53,581
(yue)但係對我嚟講
(en) But for me,

131
00:10:53,631 --> 00:10:57,602
(yue)佢係重要嘅同伴託付畀我嘅貴重物品嚟𠿪
(en) it is a valuable item entrusted to me by an important comrade.

132
00:10:57,659 --> 00:11:01,763
(yue)我一直都諗住將來有日可以將佢還返畀你
(en) I've always planned to return it to you someday.

133
00:11:10,142 --> 00:11:12,777
(yue)明明呢樣嘢根本就一啲都唔重要
(en) Clearly, this thing is not important at all.

134
00:11:32,607 --> 00:11:33,934
(yue)欣梅爾仲未得嗱？
(en) Has Xinmel not arrived yet?

135
00:11:34,843 --> 00:11:37,522
(yue)你冇頭髮花時間打扮都冇意思啦
(en) Without hair, there's no point in spending time on styling.

136
00:11:38,429 --> 00:11:40,896
(yue)光頭都有光頭嘅堅持㗎
(en) Even a bald head has its own sense of pride.

137
00:11:48,232 --> 00:11:49,125
(yue)好喇
(en) Alright.

138
00:11:49,176 --> 00:11:51,925
(yue)我哋而家去睇半世紀流星喇
(en) Let's go see the half-century meteor now.

139
00:12:00,185 --> 00:12:02,555
(yue)你變到好有威嚴喎，海塔
(en) You've become so dignified, Haita.

140
00:12:02,895 --> 00:12:05,071
(yue)因為我係聖都嘅主教啊
(en) Because I am the bishop of the Holy City.

141
00:12:05,095 --> 00:12:07,588
(yue)芙莉蓮，你真係一啲都冇變啊
(en) Flilian, you really haven't changed at all.

142
00:12:08,311 --> 00:12:09,835
(yue)唔好摸我個頭啦
(en) Don't touch my head.

143
00:12:11,561 --> 00:12:13,850
(yue)艾冉你個樣冇乜點變過啊
(en) Airan, you haven't changed much.

144
00:12:14,508 --> 00:12:16,681
(yue)係咩？睇落冇變呀？
(en) Really? You seem unchanged.

145
00:12:16,941 --> 00:12:18,656
(yue)不愧係矮人族啊
(en) As expected of the dwarves.

146
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:21,726
(yue)係噉，你話睇得更加清嘅地方喺邊啊？
(en) So, where is that place with a clearer view?

147
00:12:21,777 --> 00:12:22,708
(yue)嗯？
(en) Hmm?

148
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:24,375
(yue)而家就出發去呀？
(en) Shall we set off now?

149
00:12:24,567 --> 00:12:26,788
(yue)距離出現半世紀流星嘅時期
(en) There is still some time until the half-century meteor appears,

150
00:12:26,839 --> 00:12:28,528
(yue)應該仲有段時間喎
(en) it should be a while.

151
00:12:28,660 --> 00:12:29,428
(yue)嗯
(en) Hmm.

152
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:32,564
(yue)因為要由呢度行一個禮拜過去㗎
(en) Because it takes about a week to walk from here.

153
00:12:33,041 --> 00:12:34,863
(yue)咩話？要行咁遠？
(en) What? We have to walk that far?

154
00:12:35,303 --> 00:12:39,049
(yue)真係吖，噉折磨老人家㗎
(en) Indeed, that's truly tormenting for us old folks.

155
00:12:42,523 --> 00:12:44,143
(yue)好懷念啊
(en) I miss those days.

156
00:12:44,455 --> 00:12:48,029
(yue)而家噉樣行，就好似返返去嗰陣噉
(en) Walking like this feels just like the old days.

157
00:12:52,619 --> 00:12:55,530
(yue)我哋去咗好多唔同嘅地方旅行
(en) We've journeyed to many different places.

158
00:12:56,244 --> 00:12:58,590
(yue)所有嘢都覺得好新鮮
(en) Everything felt so new.

159
00:12:59,345 --> 00:13:01,556
(yue)而且睇落好耀眼
(en) And it looked dazzling.

160
00:13:26,094 --> 00:13:29,001
(yue)喺我咁多美麗嘅回憶入面
(en) Among all my beautiful memories,

161
00:13:29,052 --> 00:13:31,421
(yue)一直都有你哋陪住我
(en) you've always been there for me.

162
00:13:34,346 --> 00:13:35,454
(yue)我一直
(en) I've always

163
00:13:36,073 --> 00:13:40,390
(yue)都好期待我哋所有人可以再次聚埋一齊㗎
(en) eagerly anticipating the day when all of us can reunite.

164
00:13:40,414 --> 00:13:42,708
(yue)好多謝你啊，芙莉蓮
(en) Thank you so much, Flilian.

165
00:13:43,487 --> 00:13:45,390
(yue)都係多得你
(en) It's all thanks to you.

166
00:13:45,414 --> 00:13:49,150
(yue)我先可以體驗到最後一次開心嘅冒險
(en) Because of you, I was able to experience one final, joyful adventure.

167
00:14:12,766 --> 00:14:14,504
(yue)好靚啊
(en) So beautiful.

168
00:14:41,679 --> 00:14:45,080
(yue)欣梅爾佢，就嗰陣一定覺得好幸福㗎喇
(en) Xinmel must have felt incredibly blessed back then.

169
00:14:46,783 --> 00:14:47,892
(yue)真係噉咩？
(en) Really?

170
00:14:55,103 --> 00:14:58,360
(yue)聽講嗰個女仔係欣梅爾大人嘅同伴嚟啊
(en) I heard that the girl is a companion of Lord Xinmel.

171
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,829
(yue)但係睇落一啲都唔傷心𠸏
(en) Yet she doesn't appear sorrowful at all.

172
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,494
(yue)真係好無情啊
(en) Truly heartless.

173
00:15:03,969 --> 00:15:05,041
(yue)哎吔…
(en) Oh dear...

174
00:15:05,065 --> 00:15:07,354
(yue)我哋兩個睇落都唔傷心喎
(en) The two of us don't seem sad either.

175
00:15:07,405 --> 00:15:09,155
(yue)主教，你莊重啲啦
(en) Bishop, be more dignified.

176
00:15:09,179 --> 00:15:10,530
(yue)你真係冇人性啊！
(en) You truly lack any humanity!

177
00:15:11,425 --> 00:15:13,071
(yue)畀人秒殺啊
(en) You got taken out in seconds.

178
00:15:37,366 --> 00:15:38,619
(yue)因為我根本…
(en) Because I simply...

179
00:15:39,112 --> 00:15:41,119
(yue)一啲都唔了解欣梅爾佢
(en) don't understand Xinmel at all.

180
00:15:53,934 --> 00:15:55,452
(yue)我哋只不過係…
(en) We are simply...

181
00:15:55,705 --> 00:15:57,413
(yue)一齊旅行咗十年吒嘛
(en) having traveled together for ten years.

182
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,881
(yue)我明明知道人類嘅壽命
(en) I clearly know that the lifespan of humans

183
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:08,920
(yue)不嬲都好短
(en) have always been very short.

184
00:16:10,367 --> 00:16:11,650
(yue)點解冇諗過…
(en) Why didn't we ever consider...

185
00:16:12,773 --> 00:16:14,654
(yue)多啲去了解下佢呢？
(en) getting to understand them more?

186
00:16:24,318 --> 00:16:26,400
(yue)唔好摸我個頭啦
(en) Don't touch my head.

187
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,890
(yue)我都係時候要返去聖都㗎喇
(en) It's time for me to head back to the Holy City.

188
00:16:41,503 --> 00:16:44,060
(yue)等我再好好睇下你哋個樣啦
(en) Let me take one more good look at your faces.

189
00:16:44,702 --> 00:16:46,673
(yue)今次係我哋最後一次見面喇
(en) This is our final meeting.

190
00:16:47,296 --> 00:16:48,693
(yue)你係咪唔舒服啊？
(en) Are you feeling unwell?

191
00:16:48,886 --> 00:16:51,569
(yue)飲酒飲得太痛搞到周身病痛
(en) Drinking too much has left you in pain all over.

192
00:16:51,593 --> 00:16:53,108
(yue)而家報應到哩？
(en) Is karma finally catching up?

193
00:16:54,541 --> 00:16:57,793
(yue)如果你哋有日去開聖都，記得帶支酒
(en) If you ever visit the Holy City, remember to bring some wine.

194
00:16:57,817 --> 00:16:59,121
(yue)去我墳度拜我啊
(en) and pay homage at my grave.

195
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:03,723
(yue)海塔你，真係一啲都唔驚死咩？
(en) Haita, are you truly not afraid of death?

196
00:17:05,957 --> 00:17:09,586
(yue)我哋幾個係拯救世界嘅勇者隊成員嚟𠺢嘛
(en) We are members of the heroic team that saved the world, after all.

197
00:17:09,766 --> 00:17:13,080
(yue)死咗之後，唔使問一定係上天堂享福
(en) After death, there's no question we'll be enjoying heaven.

198
00:17:14,182 --> 00:17:15,643
(yue)我都係為咗噉樣
(en) That's precisely why I

199
00:17:15,693 --> 00:17:17,799
(yue)先會同你哋一齊去戰鬥㗎咋
(en) ended up fighting with you all.

200
00:17:18,295 --> 00:17:19,799
(yue)你個酒肉和尚
(en) You meat-eating monk.

201
00:17:22,132 --> 00:17:23,568
(yue)係噉，我走先喇
(en) Alright, I'm leaving now.

202
00:17:32,021 --> 00:17:34,680
(yue)好啦，我都係時候要走喇
(en) Alright, it's time for me to leave too.

203
00:17:35,662 --> 00:17:37,635
(yue)繼續收集魔法之類？
(en) Continue collecting magic or something?

204
00:17:37,938 --> 00:17:40,028
(yue)嗯，呢個都係目的之一
(en) Yes, that's one of my purposes.

205
00:17:40,822 --> 00:17:43,488
(yue)但係我仲想去試下多啲了解人類
(en) But I also want to try to understand humans better.

206
00:17:45,878 --> 00:17:46,733
(yue)乜係？
(en) What?

207
00:17:47,982 --> 00:17:50,183
(yue)我有一件事想同你商量啊
(en) I have something I'd like to discuss with you.

208
00:17:50,343 --> 00:17:52,118
(yue)因為我係用魔法𠺢嘛
(en) Because I use magic,

209
00:17:52,169 --> 00:17:55,030
(yue)所以如果身邊有個強大嘅先鋒就好喇
(en) so it would be nice to have a strong vanguard by my side.

210
00:17:55,081 --> 00:17:56,609
(yue)你都係放過我啦
(en) You should just let me be.

211
00:17:57,301 --> 00:18:00,835
(yue)我已經年紀大到揮唔郁把斧頭喇
(en) I'm already too old to even swing an axe.

212
00:18:03,363 --> 00:18:05,698
(yue)唔好噉嘅表情啦，芙莉蓮
(en) Don't make that face, Flilian.

213
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:09,174
(yue)人嘅一生喺歲老之後嘅時間
(en) The later part of one's life after aging

214
00:18:09,224 --> 00:18:11,142
(yue)比想象中要長嘅
(en) is longer than we think.

215
00:18:13,330 --> 00:18:13,916
(yue)係呀？
(en) Really?

216
00:18:14,916 --> 00:18:16,643
(yue)噉再見喇，艾冉
(en) Well then, goodbye, Airan.

217
00:18:17,429 --> 00:18:19,017
(yue)啊，再見
(en) Ah, goodbye.

218
00:18:53,485 --> 00:18:56,945
(yue)（第一話：冒險結束）
(en) (Episode One: The Adventure Ends)

219
00:19:00,984 --> 00:19:02,718
(yue)係頭先棵樹呀？
(en) Was that the tree from earlier?

220
00:19:02,769 --> 00:19:05,078
(yue)每次嚟呢個森林都會蕩失路
(en) Every time I come to this forest, I end up getting lost.

221
00:19:05,196 --> 00:19:06,425
(yue)呢度係邊度啊？
(en) Where is this place?

222
00:19:07,105 --> 00:19:10,310
(yue)（勇者欣梅爾死之後20年）
（中央諸國）
 （聖都修特拉爾郊外）
(en) (20 years after Hero Xinmel's death)
(Central Nations)
(Outskirts of the Holy City, Xiu Telar)

223
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,020
(yue)請問你係咪揾緊咩啊？
(en) Excuse me, are you searching for something?

224
00:19:18,697 --> 00:19:20,446
(yue)請問係咪有咩事啊？
(en) May I ask, is there a problem?

225
00:19:21,352 --> 00:19:25,033
(yue)噉𠸏，我喺度揾緊一個
叫海塔嘅人嘅屋企啊
(en) Well, I'm looking for the house of someone named Haita.

226
00:19:25,084 --> 00:19:27,839
(yue)原來你係海塔大人嘅客人呀？
(en) So you're a guest of Lord Haita?

227
00:19:30,819 --> 00:19:33,020
(yue)你個酒肉和尚仲好地地喎
(en) You, the meat-eating monk, are still quite decent.

228
00:19:34,804 --> 00:19:36,561
(yue)想好有型噉死
(en) Want to go out in style.

229
00:19:36,612 --> 00:19:38,637
(yue)都唔係件容易嘅事嚟㗎
(en) That's not an easy thing to do.

230
00:19:38,688 --> 00:19:41,050
(yue)我仲買咗酒諗住放喺你個墳前面
(en) I even bought some wine, intending to place it in front of your grave.

231
00:19:41,608 --> 00:19:42,810
(yue)飲唔飲返杯啊？
(en) Care for a drink?

232
00:19:42,867 --> 00:19:44,770
(yue)我已經戒咗酒喇
(en) I've already quit drinking.

233
00:19:45,129 --> 00:19:45,890
(yue)係呀？
(en) Really?

234
00:19:46,736 --> 00:19:48,839
(yue)而家先開始改過自新
(en) I'm only now beginning to reform.

235
00:19:48,890 --> 00:19:51,699
(yue)我諗女神大人應該都唔會就噉原諒你
(en) I don't think the Goddess would simply forgive you just like that.

236
00:19:58,953 --> 00:20:00,519
(yue)真係唔該晒你啊
(en) Thank you so much.

237
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,009
(yue)佢係邊個啊？
(en) Who is he?

238
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:08,479
(yue)佢個名叫做費倫
(en) His name is Feilun.

239
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:12,209
(yue)係南方諸國嘅戰爭留落嚟嘅孤兒
(en) An orphan left over from the wars in the southern nations.

240
00:20:13,553 --> 00:20:14,760
(yue)好唔似你喎
(en) That doesn't quite match you.

241
00:20:15,306 --> 00:20:18,353
(yue)你不嬲都唔係嗰種會熱心助人嘅人嚟
(en) You've never been the kind of person who's eager to help others.

242
00:20:18,748 --> 00:20:20,233
(yue)同欣梅爾好唔同
(en) Not at all like Xinmel.

243
00:20:22,905 --> 00:20:25,479
(yue)芙莉蓮，你嚟我呢度做咩啊？
(en) Flilian, what brings you here?

244
00:20:26,293 --> 00:20:28,633
(yue)我去聖都買嘢順便嚟睇你
(en) I went to the Holy City to shop, and I took the opportunity to see you.

245
00:20:28,980 --> 00:20:32,280
(yue)因為我而家會盡量
同旅途中遇到嘅人多啲互動
(en) Because these days, I try to interact more with the people I meet on my journeys.

246
00:20:33,765 --> 00:20:36,467
(yue)再加上，我仲爭海塔你好多人情
(en) Moreover, I still owe you a lot of favors, Haita.

247
00:20:36,605 --> 00:20:38,447
(yue)所以想喺你死之前還畀你
(en) So I wish to return something to you before you pass away.

248
00:20:42,121 --> 00:20:44,137
(yue)係噉有件事想拜託你
(en) I have a request for you.

249
00:20:44,195 --> 00:20:44,727
(yue)嗯？
(en) Hmm?

250
00:20:45,669 --> 00:20:47,330
(yue)你有冇諗過收徒弟？
(en) Have you ever thought about taking on an apprentice?

251
00:20:49,487 --> 00:20:52,597
(yue)費倫佢，好有做一個魔法師嘅資質
(en) Feilun has the aptitude to be a great magician.

252
00:20:53,224 --> 00:20:56,097
(yue)你可唔可以帶埋佢同你一齊去旅行啊？
(en) Could you take him along with you on your journey?

253
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:00,640
(yue)對唔住啊，海塔
(en) I'm sorry, Haita.

254
00:21:00,691 --> 00:21:02,075
(yue)我冇辦法應承你
(en) I can't commit to that.

255
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:04,122
(yue)佢會成為我嘅負累
(en) He would just become a liability to me.

256
00:21:05,638 --> 00:21:09,123
(yue)你都知見習魔法師
喺實戰嘅死亡率有幾高㗎啦
(en) You know how high the death rate is for apprentice magicians in battle.

257
00:21:10,364 --> 00:21:12,059
(yue)朋友交託個細路畀我
(en) A friend entrusted me with the youngster.

258
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:13,931
(yue)我唔打算送佢去死啊
(en) I don't intend to let him die.

259
00:21:16,907 --> 00:21:17,990
(yue)原來係噉
(en) I see.

260
00:21:18,895 --> 00:21:20,990
(yue)係噉，我想拜託你另一件事
(en) Alright, I have another favor to ask of you.

261
00:21:26,448 --> 00:21:29,850
(yue)呢本係由賢者埃維希個墓出土嘅文物
(en) This book is an artifact excavated from the tomb of the sage Evishi.

262
00:21:30,645 --> 00:21:32,381
(yue)聽講呢本魔道書
(en) I heard that this grimoire

263
00:21:32,432 --> 00:21:34,938
(yue)入面記載住而家已經失傳咗
(en) contains inscriptions that are now lost.

264
00:21:34,962 --> 00:21:37,448
(yue)可以將死者復活嘅不死魔法
(en) The necromancy that can revive the dead.

265
00:21:37,975 --> 00:21:41,049
(yue)我唔覺得呢個世界上會有呢啲噉嘅魔法囖
(en) I don't believe such magic exists in this world.

266
00:21:41,488 --> 00:21:45,161
(yue)所以我想你幫我手解讀呢個魔道書
(en) So I want you to help me decipher this grimoire.

267
00:21:45,543 --> 00:21:46,822
(yue)可唔可以啊？
(en) Can you do that?

268
00:21:47,476 --> 00:21:49,662
(yue)呢啲係用圖畫做嘅暗號？
(en) Are these secret codes made out of drawings?

269
00:21:49,713 --> 00:21:52,163
(yue)呢個時代嘅人真係好鍾意呢啲嘢
(en) People in this era really have a fondness for these things.

270
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:55,380
(yue)只要畀五六年我都得𠸏
(en) I could manage it in just five or six years.

271
00:21:56,020 --> 00:21:57,191
(yue)係噉樣呀？
(en) Is that so?

272
00:21:58,117 --> 00:22:01,019
(yue)但係解讀呢啲嘢之後，你打算做咩啊？
(en) But after deciphering these, what do you intend to do?

273
00:22:01,043 --> 00:22:03,476
(yue)你之前唔係話過你唔怕死㗎咩？
(en) Didn't you say that you weren't afraid of death?

274
00:22:03,777 --> 00:22:05,843
(yue)我噉做係有兩個理由
(en) I have two reasons for doing this.

275
00:22:06,289 --> 00:22:07,454
(yue)第一個係
(en) The first is

276
00:22:07,504 --> 00:22:10,523
(yue)我之前喺你哋面前噉講即係讕有型
(en) that my previous words in front of you were merely for show.

277
00:22:11,083 --> 00:22:15,120
(yue)另一個理由係我比起之前變得更加怕死
(en) The other reason is that I have grown more fearful of death than before.

278
00:22:16,047 --> 00:22:18,445
(yue)我唔使長生不死
(en) I don't need eternal life.

279
00:22:18,469 --> 00:22:19,720
(yue)只想長命啲
(en) I only wish to live a bit longer.

280
00:22:20,422 --> 00:22:22,340
(yue)長少少已經夠㗎喇
(en) A little extra longevity is enough.

281
00:22:22,391 --> 00:22:24,420
(yue)我想要多啲啲時間
(en) I desire more time.

282
00:22:28,341 --> 00:22:30,201
(yue)而且聖典都有寫啦
(en) And the scriptures also mention it.

283
00:22:30,252 --> 00:22:32,498
(yue)人要健健康康噉生活
(en) That people should live healthily.

284
00:22:32,576 --> 00:22:35,421
(yue)長壽咪係最好嘅證明囖，芙莉蓮
(en) Longevity is the greatest testament, Flilian.

285
00:22:35,798 --> 00:22:37,294
(yue)你個酒肉和尚
(en) You meat-eating monk.

286
00:22:39,681 --> 00:22:40,508
(yue)啊，係喇
(en) Ah, indeed.

287
00:22:40,967 --> 00:22:43,786
(yue)喺你解讀嘅空檔時間都冇問題㗎
(en) There's no issue as long as it fits into the gaps during your deciphering.

288
00:22:43,844 --> 00:22:47,000
(yue)你可唔可以幫手教下費倫佢點用魔法啊？
(en) Could you help instruct Feilun on how to use magic?

289
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:48,927
(yue)因為我係個僧侶
(en) Because I'm a monk.

290
00:22:48,978 --> 00:22:51,286
(yue)所以真係唔係好識教佢
(en) So I'm not very good at teaching him.

291
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:54,140
(yue)如果淨係教下都得𠸏
(en) Even just teaching him the basics would suffice.

292
00:23:02,188 --> 00:23:03,151
(yue)揾到喇
(en) Found it.

293
00:23:04,731 --> 00:23:06,630
(yue)要揾你真係唔容易啊
(en) It's really not easy to find you.

294
00:23:07,038 --> 00:23:09,231
(yue)你平時都係喺森林修行嘎？
(en) Do you normally practice in the forest?

295
00:23:09,531 --> 00:23:13,400
(yue)原來就連芙莉蓮大人
你都覺得好難先可以揾到我呀？
(en) So even Lord Flilian finds it difficult to locate me?

296
00:23:14,399 --> 00:23:16,121
(yue)海塔大人成日都話
(en) Lord Haita always says

297
00:23:16,172 --> 00:23:18,032
(yue)我呢個人冇乜存在感
(en) that I don't have much presence.

298
00:23:20,235 --> 00:23:22,505
(yue)但係我覺得噉樣唔算係一件壞事
(en) But I think that's not necessarily a bad thing.

299
00:23:24,118 --> 00:23:25,018
(yue)你都啱𠸏
(en) You're right.

300
00:23:28,243 --> 00:23:28,926
(yue)果然...
(en) As expected...

301
00:23:29,742 --> 00:23:31,982
(yue)魔力探知對佢冇乜反應咁滯
(en) Magical detection has little effect on him.

302
00:23:32,737 --> 00:23:34,775
(yue)佢操控魔力嘅技術好出色
(en) His technique in manipulating magic is outstanding.

303
00:23:36,115 --> 00:23:37,012
(yue)佢咁細個
(en) When he was just a child,

304
00:23:37,063 --> 00:23:39,455
(yue)究竟用咗幾多時間去鑽研魔法啊？
(en) just how much time did he spend delving into magic?

305
00:23:40,028 --> 00:23:41,121
(yue)海塔大人話
(en) Lord Haita said,

306
00:23:41,901 --> 00:23:43,924
(yue)我打得穿山頂嗰嚿岩石
(en) I could break through that mountain-top boulder,

307
00:23:43,975 --> 00:23:45,721
(yue)就可以自己獨當一面㗎喇
(en) then I could manage on my own.

308
00:23:46,486 --> 00:23:47,216
(yue)吓？
(en) Huh?

309
00:23:47,488 --> 00:23:49,047
(yue)海塔都識啲嘢喎
(en) Haita does know a thing or two.

310
00:23:49,098 --> 00:23:49,928
(yue)嗰嚿係...
(en) That boulder is...

311
00:23:56,269 --> 00:23:58,610
(yue)我嘅魔力會好似噉樣散開晒
(en) My magic will spread out like this completely,

312
00:23:58,688 --> 00:23:59,776
(yue)去唔到嗰嚿石
(en) and won't affect that boulder.

313
00:24:00,790 --> 00:24:01,683
(yue)原來係噉樣
(en) So that's how it works.

314
00:24:02,535 --> 00:24:05,260
(yue)係噉我應該點樣修行先至好啊？
(en) So how should I train properly then?

315
00:24:05,888 --> 00:24:06,539
(yue)喂
(en) Hey.

316
00:24:06,877 --> 00:24:08,299
(yue)我想問你一樣嘢先
(en) I want to ask you something first.

317
00:24:09,582 --> 00:24:10,948
(yue)你鍾唔鍾意魔法？
(en) Do you like magic?

318
00:24:11,902 --> 00:24:13,662
(yue)我諗我都算鍾意𠸏
(en) I suppose I do.

319
00:24:16,221 --> 00:24:17,609
(yue)同我一模一樣啊
(en) Just like me.

320
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,886
(yue)（第二話，不見得一定是靠魔法…）
唔係一定要靠魔法㗎
(en) (Episode Two: It Isn't Necessarily About Relying on Magic...)
It's not all about relying on magic.
